<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL41">
<l>vāṉuḷā raṟiya lākā vāṉavā veṉpa rākil</l>
<l>tēṉulān tuḷapa mālaic ceṉṉiyā yeṉpa rākil</l>
<l>ūṉamā yiṉakaḷ ceyyu mūṉakā rakarka ḷēlum</l>
<l>pōṉakañ ceyta cēṭan taruvarēl puṉita maṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if they commit evil or cause evil to be committed,</l>
<l rend="indent">if they say, ‘O Celestial who cannot be known by the sky-dwellers!’</l>
<l rend="indent">if they say, ‘O You whose head [is adorned with] tulasī garlands in which honey spreads!’</l>
<l>if [those people] give the remnants [after] having eaten</l>
<l>[one becomes] purified that very day!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
